Auth:
POST: /api/auth/register
POST: /api/auth/login (simple dummy simulation)

Passenger:

POST: /api/passenger/request-ride
GET: /api/passenger/ride-status/{rideId}
GET: /api/passenger/ride-history
GET: /api/passenger/available-drivers (my assumption)

Driver:

GET: /api/driver/pending-requests
POST: /api/driver/respond/{rideId} -> (actions: accept/reject)
POST: /api/driver/start-ride/{rideId}
POST: /api/driver/complete-ride/{rideId}
POST: /api/driver/set-status